EN: The average per person spending at this restaurant is around 50 yuan.

ZH: 去年公司的人均销售额增长了20%。
EN: The company's average sales per capita increased by 20% last year.

ZH: 这家酒店的人均入住率很高。
EN: The average occupancy rate of this hotel is very high.

